replies.body:
Depending what rank you finished on at the end of ranked season will show your border. So say if you are plat 3 solo/duo queue but are gold in flex, the last ranked game will determine the border that appears in the loading screen and waiting in lobby. So if your last ranked game was solo it will show your plat border however if your last ranked game was flex it will show your gold border that you acquired at the end of ranked season. However when people will view your profile it will show your highest rank even if it is flex. So if your last ranked game was silver for your example it will show the silver border in loading screen and lobby. 

However if you say that even tho your highest rank is gold 4 and it isn't showing on your profile  it might just be a bug. {{sticker:sg-ahri-2}} 

Hope this helped to explain things :D
